rence calls/ background checks</div><div>    📝 Offer&nbsp; </div><div><br></div><div>If you want to dig deeper into Blocknative, please explore our <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9engR8mowKMratKYMBzOXQ" class="postings-link">YouTube channel</a> and <a href="https://www.blocknative.com/blog" class="postings-link">blog</a>: </div><div>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.blocknative.com/blog/blockchain-101" class="postings-link">Blockchain 101</a></div><div>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.blocknative.com/blog/series-a" class="postings-link">Series A Announcement</a></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px">#LI-Remote </span></div><p><figure><iframe style="width: 500px; height: 281px;" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/ZYeJBflHZvQ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></figure></p>]]></description>
