&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Okcoin is looking for an Affiliate Marketing Associate to support strategy and execution for our growing global affiliate program. You’ll be responsible for supporting the management of the affiliate program. You’ll work to scale user acquisition, as well as work with cross-functional partners to level up reporting and program capabilities. The right candidate will have experience managing an affiliate program, working within Impact Radius, as well as good to strong experience working with cross functional partners to ensure key channel initiatives are executed and prioritized.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
