&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unlimited vacation / sick days &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;because everyone deserves time for R&amp;amp;R&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
